These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
4 different games are played: go, snooker, whist, domino
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, photographer, scientist, writer
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, cain, davidoff, dunhill
4 different pets are kept: cat, fish, frog, rabbit
1. the photographer is the person playing go##1
2. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
3. the davidoff-smoker is the designer##1
4. the person playing domino is on the right of the photographer##1
5. the scientist is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
6. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
7. the photographer is the owner of the cat##1
8. the cain-smoker is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
9. the person playing domino is on the left of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Game         | go  | domino  | snooker | whist |
| Job           | photographer | designer | writer  | scientist  |
| Cigar   | dunhill       | davidoff      | montecristo | cain      |
| Pet           | cat          | fish     | frog    | rabbit     |

