.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
House: ranch-style, art-deco, futuristic, cape-cod
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, kiwi, orange, papaya
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, rock-climbing, camping, puzzles
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, ice-hockey, volleyball, water-polo
1. the person eating broccoli is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the person eating orange is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
6. the futuristic house is the person who's hobby is camping##1
7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the art-deco house##1
8. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
9. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| House      | futuristic     | ranch-style       | art-deco | cape-cod        |
| Food          | papaya     | kiwi       | orange   | broccoli   |
| Hobby   | camping      | rock-climbing       | puzzles     | fishing    |
| Sport         | volleyball | water-polo | baseball | ice-hockey |

