.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, dannemann, dunhill, havana
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, november, june, december
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, horror, musical, scientific
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, lizard, mouse, pony
 1. the havana-smoker is the owner of the pony##1
 2. the dunhill-smoker is on the far right##1
 3. the person watching musical movies is on the far right##1
 4. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 5. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
 6. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
 7. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 8. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 9. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
10. the dunhill-smoker is the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| Cigar      | dannemann | davidoff       | havana        | dunhill        |
| Birthday           | november   | june | may   | december |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure     | horror    | scientific | musical        |
| Pet           | mouse         | hedgehog  | pony       | lizard         |

