6. the fan of funk is on the right of the colonial house##1
7. the futuristic house is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
8. the australian is on the far right##1
9. the person who's birthday is in october is the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
| House           | colonial   | farmhouse  | futuristic | modern |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | funk       | d&b       | ambient     |
| Nationality   | thai       | turkish    | dutch     | australian  |
| Birthday           | january     | october | august     | september         |

