.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, hiking, cooking, sudoku
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, romance, spy, superhero
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, december, september, june
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, biathlon, cycling, handball
1. the person watching spy movies is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
6. the person who's sport is handball is the person who's birthday is in september##1
7. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
8. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
9. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Hobby           | chess  | cooking    | hiking | sudoku |
| Movie-Genre   | spy      | romance    | drama         | superhero    |
| Birthday   | december   | february     | september          | june      |
| Sport         | biathlon | basketball | handball      | cycling      |

