.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-6::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, card-games, cooking, traveling
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, dancer, doctor, writer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, mystery, scientific, thriller
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, mirinda, iced-tea, juice
 1. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person watching mystery movies##1
 3. the accountant is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 4. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is the writer##1
 6. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 7. the doctor is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 8. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the doctor is on the far left##1
10. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Hobby          | puzzles  | traveling | cooking     | card-games |
| Job           | doctor  | writer      | accountant | dancer    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | scientific  | fantasy    | thriller  |
| Beverage           | iced-tea   | juice       | 7up       | mirinda      |

