.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, iced-tea, mirinda
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, rose, daisy, azalea
City: new-york, boston, berlin, paris
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, quad-bike, scooter, taxi
 1. the person traveling to new-york is the person who growsrose##1
 2. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
 4. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
 5. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
 6. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
 7. the person traveling to new-york is the person driving the scooter##1
 8. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
 9. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
10. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage    | coffee | fanta     | iced-tea    | mirinda |
| Flower       | tulip | daisy    | azalea | rose |
| City         | boston   | berlin  | paris        | new-york    |
| Transport   | taxi   | quad-bike | airplane    | scooter |

