2. the fan of d&b is the person watching western movies##1
3. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
5. the person watching western movies is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
6. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
7. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person driving the bus##1
8. the person driving the scooter is the fan of reggae##1
9. the person driving the skateboard is the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre      | d&b      | reggae         | techno        | disco      |
| Hobby           | traveling | fishing | photography  | baking  |
| Movie-Genre   | western    | musical     | time-travel | zombie     |
| Transport     | bus        | scooter     | jet-ski     | skateboard |

