6. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
7. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
8. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far right##1
9. the italian is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Birthday          | january | october     | november       | august |
