 5. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
 6. the electrician is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 7. the lawyer is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
 8. the person driving the roller is on the left of the fan of funk##1
 9. the person driving the van is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
10. the person eating garlic is the bartender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3       |     4     |
